  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The galaxy is under attack and awaits your valor and skill in the face of looming peril. Join the ranks and let your journey to bring stability and order to the outer borders of the cosmos begin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/3f0dd45d307235b04fa78d2fab74f54c.webp?t=1727452565\" width=600 height=50 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/c3c3d4a48bd903262f1b53b9299f935c.poster.avif?t=1727452565\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/c3c3d4a48bd903262f1b53b9299f935c.webm?t=1727452565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/c3c3d4a48bd903262f1b53b9299f935c.mp4?t=1727452565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mine asteroids for precious metals and minerals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harvest space clouds to discover exotic gases and chemicals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Salvage wrecks for spare parts and lost artifacts.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/e06f9bab0f3aea3632443def4d32f650.webp?t=1727452565\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/3f8989e79a1b26caa92558106ce6f135.poster.avif?t=1727452565\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/3f8989e79a1b26caa92558106ce6f135.webm?t=1727452565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/3f8989e79a1b26caa92558106ce6f135.mp4?t=1727452565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in battles against local factions for loot, experience, and glory.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select the right gear to counter your enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash special abilities to turn the tide of battle in your favor.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/f21eceb80ba29acf83d0b48148dcf466.webp?t=1727452565\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/47f6918ebeadf01d0a0b9f94e1e8f4fe.poster.avif?t=1727452565\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/47f6918ebeadf01d0a0b9f94e1e8f4fe.webm?t=1727452565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/47f6918ebeadf01d0a0b9f94e1e8f4fe.mp4?t=1727452565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit crew members to assist you on your journey, even while offline.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft resources, fuse powerful chipsets, and unlock scientific advancements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prioritize your upgrades to suit your playstyle, whether it's active, idle, or both.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/1fdc89f38ba22c132ce425788ecef988.webp?t=1727452565\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/11848b10b4ec30d62bbc561e70199e19.poster.avif?t=1727452565\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/11848b10b4ec30d62bbc561e70199e19.webm?t=1727452565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2530570/extras/11848b10b4ec30d62bbc561e70199e19.mp4?t=1727452565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your ship modules to improve your gathering and combat capabilities.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up your crew members to unlock new mechanics and perks</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join the ranks of the galactic empire and prepare to stand against the impending invasion!</strong></p>",
